Name: Sushi Rush
About the game: About This game is a simulation fast food Sushi restaurant game. First of all, you have to play the role of the receptionist and firmly remember what the guests ordered. Only the correct dishes can bring income, and the wrong dishes must be compensated for the guests. Secondly, Serve guests the right ehoumaki rolls, the right color of rice and the right color wrapped filling. Third, you have to prepare essertd for the guests, according to the requirements of the guests, if it is wrong, it may lead to failure. Fourth, you have to make rice for the guests. The guests will ask for different cookness, etc., and you need to record them immediately. Feature The difficulty of the game increases dramatically as the levels increase, making it ideal for those who are more than willing to challenge themselves.
